<font color="#FF0000">WORKING WITH OFFICERS.</font><br>
<tt>Thu Nov 13  0:43:29 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I tried to post this yesterday, but had a glitch.  Anyway, here it is:<br><br>
We worked together as an aircrew, and even though the officers were flying, they saw to it that we got some stick time just so, in case they were hit, someone might handle the chopper.  We had good feelings, until someone tried to pull rank or something like that (yup, it did happen a time or two).  But when a mission came, rank went out the window.  I told those pilots who let me fly a bit that I was sure I could land that chopper (an HH-53C Super Jolly) in one,... or two, or three pieces.  
